				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Riwwi!!<a name="30798"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 26 04 11:51 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>as alot of you know lots of riwwi is around level 60s zone and some REALLY nice stuff can drop there (in the arena)  heres what ive found works really well
<br />

<br />
up in the stands, there are Mastruq Warfeinds and they range anywhere from 48-62 in level....well you can go into the tunnels on 1 of the sides to pull, but mezz it on the pull, run out and find one of the bleachers that is all mastruqs because they dont all agro when you charm one. you have to stand on the stones to be able to see it and be in range, then charm one of them, it will come down to you, the mezz will break, then you will have some mobs to kite..
<br />

<br />
note it takes skill to kite here and decent resists cuz stuff casts...sometimes i just pull all the bleachers on opposite side of officiater (i only take her once the arena is cleared because of her snare) and you gotta note that sometimes the mastruq warfeinds will be too high to charm, in which case just pull one till its your pet....and just wear down the other mobs with it till its low, break charm, kill it, then finish the others off by charming another or chanting them to death depending on hp. all i know is some pretty decent stuff drops here and one of the converted laborer dropped a really nice caster tunic and i sold the loots to it for 50k (the laborers have  the long corpse time...like 24mins)
<br />

<br />
i just gotta share what ive found here its a really nice place and it gets even better once you know what your doing</span></td>
